{"tid":1642463,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[和理非] 我掩護你個掩護","createTime":"2019-10-09T17:17:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-09T17:21:16.000Z","uid":320097,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"1f31fb2e66d455b8ac1de396c204b9f2e6a0ebbc","tid":1642463,"uid":320097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T17:17:18.000Z","msg":"而家有人話裝修要停係因為民意逆轉<br />\n<br />\n事實上民意依然硬過連仔下面<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n只係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">中間友</span>/<span style=\"color: teal;\">淺藍</span></span>對<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">裝修裝飾</span>好敏感 好難接受<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但唔可以停 因為無依d勇武成個運動就完架啦 條7婆只會更加囂張<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之前四色勇武的確好正 文宣都好足 但依然有人唔知 <span style=\"color: red;\">因為真係有人有字都唔睇</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁有咩可以再核爆d 就係將<span style=\"font-size: large;\">2D變3D</span> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">黑裝修 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">紅裝飾</span> <br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">藍罷買</span> <br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">黃支持</span> </span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">去彌敦道<br />\n去夏愨道叫爆佢</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">每次勇武都係第一時間到現場rb掩護 <br />\n仲要被逗就賴嘢 <br />\n仲要俾d藍絲叼嚟叼去 你唔介意我都心痛啦 </span><br />\n<br />\n今次我地掩護佢個掩護 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">四色勇武 抗爭有理 <br />\n不分化 不割席 不篤灰 <br />\n香港人 反抗</span></span><br />\n<br />\nP牌仔唔識嘢 有錯就大大力"},{"pid":"1f37be3303729756737758f4f394da32cf19d573","tid":1642463,"uid":320097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T17:20:04.000Z","msg":"推唔郁都推"},{"pid":"d2c2ca66351904663552ed2b02af7e78cf661376","tid":1642463,"uid":320097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T17:20:24.000Z","msg":"1/5"},{"pid":"2be2fa8306071a94a94375e9c09faf6421c076df","tid":1642463,"uid":320097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T17:20:40.000Z","msg":"2/5"},{"pid":"5014003a1795bc8bc7ff4eb2ecea645c93936727","tid":1642463,"uid":320097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T17:20:53.000Z","msg":"3/5"},{"pid":"5234785aaecf8cce04fa5106044f360d8995ecf0","tid":1642463,"uid":320097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T17:21:06.000Z","msg":"4/5"},{"pid":"c1ba41a527244a74709d590bb6bde69919a480af","tid":1642463,"uid":320097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T17:21:16.000Z","msg":"5/5"}]}